scene.message:
Maki: So that was a{nl}
Persona? "Persona"...{nl}
the power of the mind...{nl}
another self... huh...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The word comes from{nl}
the Latin for "mask," the{nl}
root of "personal."{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: So the human mind{nl}
holds demons and angels{nl}
both... is that it?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Poetically speaking.{nl}
But: an eye for an eye,{nl}
a tooth for a tooth —{nl}
fight demons with demons.{waitkey}The how doesn't matter.{nl}
It works.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...I can do it!{nl}
Let's beat whatever made{nl}
the demons overflow and{nl}
take our town back!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Yes. And to do that{nl}
we need to rescue that{nl}
idiot first.{nl}
Let's go, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I won't let that{nl}
girl have her way anymore!{nl}
Right, {ctl07:1}?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
in a way Kamitori is{nl}
more dangerous than demons.{waitkey}She's the one staging{nl}
all this. Don't{nl}
forget that.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
Where are you going?{nl}
We need to rescue Inaba!{waitkey}{ret}
